I haven't gotten to be as active as I'd have liked on social this year.

But I continue to work hard, and I don't take the opportunity I've been given to do this job lightly.

There are some things I'll work on, which will be public facing, such  as my visit to Downing Street yesterday - with thanks to the Treasury.

And there'll be other things I'll work on, where to be honest, you will see no trace of me at all.

Whether you see me or whether you don't, I represent you. And it is my aspiration to be an asset to you all.

I thank you for your support.

Mr MoneyJar
